          "title": "Data minimization: reduce what you keep",
          "content_blocks": [
            {
              "type": "explain",
              "text": "Data minimization reduces risk by keeping less sensitive data. Best practice: destroy data when it’s no longer needed. If you can’t remove it, deidentify/obfuscate it."
            },
